# ==========================================================================
# 27rroses Project Gitignore Framework
# ==========================================================================

# --- Operating System System Files ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# --- Code Editor & IDE Workspaces ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# --- Local Development Servers & Logs ---
.live-server/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# --- Optional: Local Test Images (Uncomment if needed) ---
# If you drop giant temporary test photos directly into your main folders
# and don't want them tracked on GitHub, uncomment the lines below:
# test-*.jpg
# test-*.png
# assets/images/tmp/